{"tid":374766,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"父母鎖5歲養子在地下室　迫食紅蘿蔔致膚色變橙","createTime":"2017-08-26T04:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T13:56:25.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"171e2027b61dbc1825ff40d4a81ad25df3e8b5e2","tid":374766,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170825/s00005/fe8aca1702e08549f68471c0840255e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170825%2Fs00005%2Ffe8aca1702e08549f68471c0840255e9.jpg&h=d51d5b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2017年8月25日 星期五<br />\n美國猶他州一對夫婦把5歲養子鎖在地下室，迫他每天飯前要先吃紅蘿蔔，導致養子膚色變橙。夫婦被控二級虐待兒童，男孩則交由祖母照顧。<br />\n案情指受虐男童每天下午6時至翌日早上6時，會被鎖在只有約10尺乘10尺大的地下室。室內沒有光線，他只可在床墊上睡覺，僅有一張毛毯保暖。<br />\n男孩向警察說在黑暗地下室容易撞到牆壁。地下室內有老鼠和蜘蛛，地板布滿老鼠糞便，令他十分害怕。<br />\n警方又指男孩每天需要在飯前吃一碗或一袋紅蘿蔔，若未能在限時內吃完，不能吃飯和喝水。經醫生檢查後，男孩因為過量進食紅蘿蔔，皮膚略帶橙色。<br />\n警方在本月3日拘捕31歲的Brett Tobiasson和27歲的Clarissa Anne Tobiasson，懷疑他們蓄意對養子造成嚴重身體傷害。這對夫婦現被控二級虐待兒童，下月14日出庭應訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170825/s00005/1503665846145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170825%2Fs00005%2F1503665846145&d=qFtSDMDRF4sXkiswG8l1zIM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=e600ec8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170825%2Fs00005%2F1503665846145&h=3a1c5976\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170825/s00005/1503665846145</a>"},{"pid":"0a4026460dd7fab5705ccb9748c6ef78c56bbe60","tid":374766,"uid":71205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:18:49.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"eca883d6216fd4c74bacb546ca33fc084fb193c6","tid":374766,"uid":98386,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:19:09.000Z","msg":"變橙色咁正 如果日日逼蝗痴瘋食過量青菜佢咪好快變青色 到時就真真